## About this License

Octochains uses the **Business Source License (BSL) 1.1** to balance the needs of a thriving open-source community with the sustainability of the project. 

By setting a **Change Date**, we guarantee that every version of Octochains will eventually become fully Open Source (Apache 2.0). This prevents vendor lock-in while allowing the original creators to fund continued development. 

